      <data key="d1">ENGINEERING_CONTROL</data>
      <data key="d2">Engineering/control measure that shapes hospital ventilation to reduce exposure to airborne pathogens; aligns with a path principle suggesting the dominant transmission path (source to exhaust) governs risk; may be more impactful than simply increasing ACH.</data>
